        public VehicleTirePressure(double frontLeft,
                           double frontRight,
                           double backLeft,
                           double backRight)
        Initializes a new instance of the VehicleTirePressure
        Parameters:
        frontLeft - The current air pressure of the front left tire (in psi or kpa). To set unit, Vehicle.setUnitSystem(Vehicle.UnitSystem).
        frontRight - The current air pressure of the front right tire (in psi or kpa). To set unit, Vehicle.setUnitSystem(Vehicle.UnitSystem).
        backLeft - The current air pressure of the back left tire (in psi or kpa). To set unit, Vehicle.setUnitSystem(Vehicle.UnitSystem).
        backRight - The current air pressure of the back right tire (in psi or kpa). To set unit, Vehicle.setUnitSystem(Vehicle.UnitSystem).
